<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>环境市井气，氛围一步到位</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201107/8be4326c80a3460b8d1b49b5bb9d7004.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201107/bd601247e54a497f91a16f4445799c8d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201107/1a556b8b8ec0468d8e1cb17b45d7a1c4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">环境延续了一贯的风格，大红灯笼和古朴的雕花门窗，灯一亮红红火火的很有市井气息，在这样的环境氛围里涮火锅，那叫一个热闹！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>好吃到半个娱乐圈都来打卡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201107/9b1e0d26688e420590cdf6673f50e1bc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/0d6ddb81c9a347c0b6a27d2d70cd913d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201107/a9f5ae1534674bc087ca9101416c84ed.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201107/f8509b12de5b4dfb8eedb66310c0dd8d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201107/fe04d0a48ba14bcfb9cca54cda0fca1b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201107/1dc635a262bf41c1a7c61c7cba8e277f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/de816ac92d9d4e67af77dce05ab4b33f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">谭鸭血到底有多好吃呢？半个娱乐圈都来打卡了，可以说是妥妥的“<strong>明星收割机</strong>”！说不定你来这儿吃也能偶遇到你的爱豆哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201107/8391ab1c368f41b5913e7d8f7c8b488f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>经典谭鸭血红锅</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201107/96b97e894e79434696f4df31bd125104.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>招牌谭鸭血红锅</strong>是谭鸭血家的特色之一，完整的锅底里十几种底料，真材实料看得到~招牌鸭血、鹌鹑蛋、豆腐干，就连锅底的料都能吃到饱！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>•上桌先开鸿运•</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/3da303ff637b481e8ffd7d9c13e38c21.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201107/1bcd6f43c8ef4552b53606ee1da5e333.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201107/1bcd6f43c8ef4552b53606ee1da5e333.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201107/1bcd6f43c8ef4552b53606ee1da5e333.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">吃火锅也要有仪式感，<strong>开个鸿运</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>•倒入汤底咕噜咕噜•</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201107/ecdeec02e4b74363857dd4c510848afa.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">倒入<strong>四川的老鹰茶</strong>汤底，咕噜咕噜</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>•汤底能喝还不上火哦•</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/fb579abb6133454e98a0cffa8edc2c4c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">等煮沸<strong>先喝汤</strong>，茶汤完全不上火哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>•肉肉到锅里来•</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201107/22e87e05d6044188a2d2fd698742d2cc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">最后主角登场，开始涮肉肉啦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>谭公鸭血</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201107/b998d7e094384944a037f5455fe9686d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>///</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201107/8c1adf2491a04dcf9502964d24cc3dcb.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">来谭鸭血怎么能不点它家的招牌<strong>谭公鸭血</strong>呢！每片都要经过50℃高温水的浸泡，才能做到没有气孔，非常光滑~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201107/215589c1ae484e63922b703189ccb9a7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201107/a013e493755c444280817d41f72cb8f5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一份鸭血要严格是按照特有的标准，每片厚薄都一样，师傅刀工了得！<strong>现点现捞现切</strong>，每一块都滑熘熘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201107/88605cc020514dd5ad25848e51442cf2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201107/adef88067785498fbdfc631c8a8544c1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201107/ad815295fe764fbe918a5dc3f093314f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201107/8430ec0683cb4e48860adc1b904f83bd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一整盘鸭血下进去，和红油一起翻滚翻滚，还没熟已经开始想象这款舌尖上的美味了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201107/ac6564aa7df74e3aa645f4f81b2e451b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201107/5e468ca2a10240838a3cb60dfeb7730b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201107/5e468ca2a10240838a3cb60dfeb7730b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201107/5e468ca2a10240838a3cb60dfeb7730b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">煮熟后的鸭血QQ弹弹，滑熘熘的，DuangDuang的，口感相当嫩，滑得像布丁。夹稳啦，否则一不小心就熘走啦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/1444edc317c44b4ba62082ac7dd9b471.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">蘸辣油酱料吃，香！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201107/7c90c52c65d54cf685323ba4c6f06d46.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">蘸干碟吃，辣！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/10d44bda68cd44cfaff2aa0c1b789806.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">和着汤汁拌饭吃，鲜！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">用3种吃法打开鸭血，油碟、干碟、拌饭，通通都试一遍，尝尝不同口味，看看哪个是你的爱~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>谭公四宝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201107/7d89c0dcc4a64a00a4ef893f9add9734.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">想把<strong>毛肚、黄喉、鸭肠、牛百叶</strong>一网打尽的朋友们注意啦！<strong>谭公四宝</strong>那你绝对要Pick！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201107/405c903f3c4b49b38153300a5a20777e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201107/4d340100ce994400992c60f9e2e9a09e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201107/c315b4dde202450a870fa80070e2bfd2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201107/0f7263116e784f09a5465f6447f9bb98.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">点一盘一次性满足所有需求，点它点它！涮个10秒就够了，带着鲜香麻辣的红油，太馋了！我已经等不及了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>雪花肥牛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201107/410a80e86885473cab633d5a1eac06ba.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">火锅怎么能没有雪花肥牛呢，肉肉中的王牌选手！凭借嫩滑鲜香的口感成为“必点王”，每一块都在舌尖迸发出极致的肉香~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201107/4160d2a6578440c2a53f4dd17c86e13f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201107/98709ff0df3d460ab8cd9a0bb7c9618f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">放在锅里涮10秒就能吃，麻麻辣辣的带着肥牛本身的肉香，嫩香爽口，就这一口巴适得很呢！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>麻辣牛肉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201107/dada1303e7f842e0884e5ca3a98bd2f8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201107/858ee2b72c9446959dcc50ce59c6947a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201107/d55ed8a293774675a9851ed391e84138.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">喜欢川渝口味的朋友那必定要点上这款<strong>麻辣牛肉</strong>，腌制非常入味，涮了之后双重辣味加在一起，嘴里全是香辣味，带着花椒的麻爽劲儿，妙极了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>手工虾滑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201107/8f2e4ab8ca4d42dfbffef030c457b21f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201107/ad7656b00f1e46c98aaadadde7afd00a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">完全手打的<strong>手工虾滑</strong>，能感受到满满的虾肉粒，在红油锅里吸收满了汤汁，咬到的每一口都是Q弹厚实的虾肉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/3497024346894980beb4d5b0f3d85905.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">特色小吃来一份，浓浓川渝味</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>卤水拼盘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201107/d5b25fd5c9aa411caac8c30aa5806780.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">广东人的火锅桌上可不能没有卤水，<strong>卤水拼盘里有鹌鹑蛋、肥肠、郡把</strong>。万物皆可卤，卤水搭配火锅，这个CP我要嗑了！将卤水和火锅的有点结合起来，爽歪歪！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201107/5c8a8cc9e83e42a88586c1d8755149ca.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">卤水都是每天新鲜现卤的，只为食客吃到最新鲜香口的卤味。而且<strong>卤味既可以涮火锅</strong>，<strong>也可以蘸干碟吃</strong>，每一种都赋予了卤水不同的风味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>谭公酥肉&amp;手工红糖糍粑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/7cfc0c3f95dc4b00886ede59431212f5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201107/ac1e7a83745841588c769590da909a43.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">谭鸭血家的<strong>谭工酥肉</strong>简直让我太惊艳了！外酥里嫩，吃起来也完全不油不腻，一吃就是炸得很有火候，又脆又香。<strong>手工红糖糍粑</strong>也很香糯，蘸上红糖香香甜甜~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>西施冰粉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201107/9eae71c544e44b679f0565440a163a06.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">吃完火锅来一份川式冰粉解解辣吧，一勺下去冰凉凉的，让火锅结束在这一碗冰冰甜甜的冰粉中~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">●●●</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201107/26cca204722546c8b128942d655933fb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在广州就能感受地道的川味火锅，感受香辣红油的畅快，感受市井气的热闹</p>
