<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>老广惦念的羊肉煲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>怀旧羊肉煲，2种口味可选</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/84bf39bab497455bbfb1d5cce4777468.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201107/58bdb9bbcddc4a71b99e10812de6d5b6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">☑ <strong>怀旧支竹羊腩煲 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/8c32386418504af6a77519e788e18f1c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201107/3152a34a20bc4bac96b986ba5b50fe12.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201107/71d84f04d84c4bafb92d4b92f780c5b6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">怀旧支竹风味是老广挚爱。羊腩直接吃就够香，<strong>炖得皮滑肉嫩</strong>，入口爽到颤抖。配菜腐竹也不能放过！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">☑ <strong>红烧萝卜羊腩煲 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201107/1e7ced8035ce45e899025d2bd7ba1399.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201107/2342136ddf9c420c8345c64c48ebc951.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">如果爱吃辣，就可以选择这款红烧萝卜风味的羊腩煲。<strong>鲜椒的辛辣恰到好处</strong>，完美中和了羊肉的膻味，吃起来丝毫不会觉得腻味~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>秘制汤底，每日现熬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201107/9bed9d2e530b4faa828219585b5a6ca4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201107/bebb4b11382d48e581f7806894d9722b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大快朵颐前别忘了来口羊汤暖胃。汤底<strong>每日现熬</strong>，加入羊骨、竹蔗等原料<strong>熬制3小时</strong>。汤头奶白醇厚，每一口都是浓缩的羊肉精华~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>海南长大的万宁东山羊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201107/86d4e35dc6854e04a850c595b7532568.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201107/fd9854a60cd34044bf8034b7a98bf316.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">打羊煲用寻常的绵羊肉可不行，这里<strong>精选海南生长的东山羊</strong>，皮薄有弹性，炖煮过后肉嫩汤白。一煲足有一斤肉，以肥瘦均匀的羊腩为主，吃起来肥而不腻，香而不膻~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>乡下做法，土法熏制</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201107/07db318edce44ec290d38ab05422f76d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201107/9c11b0aa447143389a2c55af37200b75.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201107/4c212dc14a6445dfbabd335996374ed4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">羊肉先用乡下土法熏制，<strong>去异味的同时增加焦香味</strong>。加入老陈皮和新鲜老姜炖煮，也能起到<strong>去除羊肉膻味</strong>的作用~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>腐乳+甜酱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201107/bbb8745e485145188262a34d9a4e3ced.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/90c533efd29442329373c1d2078d3bc5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">直接吃能感受羊肉脂香，蘸上酱汁风味更佳。甜酱和腐乳<strong>恰好能中和脂肪的油腻感</strong>，吃起来满口生香！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>一煲两吃，双倍满足</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201107/79fc80676e8c46e48a934083cef526b8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201107/8b673c17d104451da49c0096c3ecb1b8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201107/6cf6875b44e3453690bac813fbdc64af.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201107/31d26a5ca9cc4d719443f8f5c579fa0e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201107/a8fe621e8c0d44b39c671aca07929813.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201107/1de45c03a488433bb9d4688232eeed76.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201107/944cd8ef46ae4f9b90f63e7cdbf3e51d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">羊肉上桌可以<strong>边吃边保温</strong>，吃得不过瘾可以追加。如果还有闲置的胃，再涮些配菜，<strong>羊肉煲、火锅一次性满足</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201107/cb1ba134468749e09173edd0ab122caf.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>来这组饭局，别错过这些新品</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201107/0219e1935334428a9b2bebae7a63373e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">『九龙饭局』坚持推陈出新，<strong>不定时更换菜单</strong>，不止羊肉煲，这次共带来了<strong>10+款秋冬新菜</strong>，款款都吸引，每一个都想打卡！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>1</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>九龙老鬼牛杂</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201107/10845265e1894e4fbb2b134f2ec9c3f4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">新鲜牛杂<strong>先用牛骨吊汤底，每日现熬，</strong>再加入师傅的<strong>秘制酱料</strong>炖煮，充分还原食材本味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/c85efd9b0ba04db09ad70fa117f7085a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201107/79dc3d2c85734e37ad198fc20dfcf10d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201107/401b3fca61b84bac95f784a977422b00.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">牛肚、牛筋、牛肠...这份牛杂<strong>分量十足，炖煮得入味</strong>，微辣的口感吃起来很过瘾~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>2</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>招牌金蒜生焗大鱼头</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201107/6c7db21178f440e38ee2d78098d04552.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201107/5d049f14b53b4608a3049aa602aa5e83.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这么大份的啫鱼头还是第一次见！一揭盖就有<strong>浓郁的蒜香</strong>扑面而来，闻到都流口水...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201107/666fc4fbea814a7f813270189a48d833.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/f7d60dca28894b03b68087f297d08ed6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">现杀的大头鱼加入酱料勐火干啫，<strong>鱼头软嫩细腻，胶原蛋白丰富</strong>，轻轻一夹就能脱骨，入口滑熘熘的像豆腐一样...</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>3</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>生啫大牛蛙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/0d45ff1107c843f2bc84445628dbab8e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">滑嫩的牛蛙肉也很适合用来干啫，<strong>咸香酱料被蛙肉充分吸收</strong>，吃起来足够香，却不会有燥气。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201107/3b908041f86943f296f171dc47c6e668.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201107/6fdf5642772d4d3e867ad4c791a5fa17.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">蛙肉挂满酱汁，入口就能感受到柔嫩、细滑，<strong>微微一抿便骨肉分离</strong>，真的好吃到舔嘴唇！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>4</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>乡下腊鸭煲仔饭</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201107/7a27f599f10c40d1a3b07ecc7fe36285.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">打羊肉煲配个煲仔饭更香！上桌还能听到滋滋声，乡下腊鸭<strong>香气十足，吃起来不会油腻</strong>，鲜香够味！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201107/4838efaee7484323a8c00ee7ca6588c6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201107/0bd13b475d1b47ed9e3208e23e7143b7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">米饭粒粒分明，<strong>均匀地包裹上了油脂和酱汁</strong>。翻到底揭开，底部饭焦<strong>表面金黄，入口又香又脆</strong>，嚼起来很过瘾~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>5</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201107/cd439c1c50c046f580fb8e8d37f53ab3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
