<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>『沙姜啫猪肚』</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201107/539cd850f2a94276868737c1ff63faa5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>『火辣辣惹味牛蛙』</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201107/42730f6175554521a53e9d3f41c53f31.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
