<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201107/ee8db80a8c134cf3b93a9c7d8a58f0af.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>既有怀旧菜式，又不乏创新口味</strong>，每一款都值得期待！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201107/00d411c387a84646924bfe54548ef2a9.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>正佳的怀旧餐馆，可以吃出人情味 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201107/a116571d77e8481aacde11cf54730dd3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
